#+TITLE: GNU G-Golf README

* GNU G-Golf

GNU G-Golf [1]
Gnome: (Guile [2] Object Library for).

** Description

G-Golf is a Guile Object Library for Gnome.

G-Golf is a library, composed of a direct binding to GObject
Introspection [3] plus a higher functionality layer, which, importing
Gnome libraries, makes GOBject classes and methods GOOPS [4] citizen.

G-Golf is a tool to develop modern graphical applications in Guile
Scheme.


** What else

G-Golf is entirely written in Guile, no C code.


** Savannah

GNU G-Golf also has a Savannah [5] project page.

